🔷 WorkItemConfig kya hai?
👉 WorkItemConfig = WorkItem ka UI + behavior control object
Approval screen ka design + rules + options
👉 Ye decide karta hai:-
Approver ko kya dikhega
Kaise approve/reject karega
Kaunse buttons honge
Comments mandatory hai ya nahi

()📦 Work Item kya hota hai? (Quick recap):-
👉 Work Item = ek task/approval/action jo kisi user ko diya jata hai
Example:-
Approval request
Access request
Manual task

()🧠 WorkItemConfig me UI + Design kaun banata hai?
--
1️⃣ Developer ka role (Main):-
👉 Developer decide karta hai:-
Kaunse fields dikhenge
Kaunse buttons (Approve/Reject) honge
Layout kaisa hoga
Logic kya hoga
💡 Ye sab XML / configuration / code me define hota hai

2️⃣ SailPoint System ka role:-
👉 SailPoint ka UI engine:-
Automatically screen generate karta hai
Config ke basis pe form dikha deta hai
💡 Matlab:-
Developer rule deta hai → SailPoint UI bana deta hai

3️⃣ WorkItemConfig ka role:-
👉 Ye control karta hai:-
UI me kya show hoga
Buttons ka behavior
Approval options
Comments required hai ya nahi
Work item kisko assign hoga
Kab expire hoga
Reminder kab jayega
Escalation hoga ya nahi


🔷 Default (Non-Custom) WorkItemConfig me kya hota hai:-
👉 SailPoint already kuch default config deta hai (tum custom define nahi karte):-

🔹 1. Approval Buttons:-
Approve
Reject
👉 Ye config decide karta hai ki:-
Kaunse actions allowed hain

🔹 2. Comments Requirement:-
Reject → comment required
Approve → optional
👉 Config control karta hai:-
Comment mandatory hai ya nahi

🔹 3. WorkItem Type:-
Approval
ManualAction
👉 UI ka behavior change hota hai type ke hisaab se

🔹 4. Form / Fields:-
👉 Approval screen pe fields dikhti hain:-
Identity Name
Requested Role
Application
Comments box
👉 Ye sab config define karta hai

🔹 5. Auto Complete Behavior:-
👉 Config decide karta hai:-
Approve → next step pe jao
Reject → workflow stop ya rollback

🔹 6. Escalation Settings:-
👉 Agar approver action nahi leta:-
Reminder bhejo
Escalate karo
👉 Ye bhi config me hota hai.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🔷 1. WorkItem State (with description):-
State	                    Description
Pending:----------Work item create ho gaya hai, abhi kisi action ka wait kar raha hai
Assigned:---------Kisi specific user ko assign ho chuka hai
InProgress:-------User ne kaam start kar diya hai
Completed:--------Task successfully complete ho gaya
Approved:---------Approval request approve ho gaya
Rejected:---------Approval reject ho gaya
Cancelled:--------Manually cancel kar diya gaya
Expired	Time:-----limit cross ho gaya (timeout)
Escalated:--------Original user ne action nahi liya → next level pe bhej diya
Suspended:--------Temporarily rok diya gaya
Terminated:-------Forcefully band kar diya gaya (workflow end)

🔷 2. WorkItem Type (with description):-
Type	                  Description
Approval:----------------Kisi request ko approve/reject karne ke liye
ManualAction:------------User ko manually koi task perform karna hai
Notification:------------Sirf info dene ke liye (no action needed)
Remediation	Issue:-------fix karne ke liye task
Certification:-----------Access review / certification process
Provisioning:------------Account create/update/delete related
Request	User:------------request process ka part
PolicyViolation:---------Policy break hone par action required

🔷 3. WorkItem Status (with description):-
Status	           Description
Open:-------------Work item abhi active hai
Closed:-----------Complete ho gaya ya band ho gaya
Pending:----------Action ka wait kar raha hai
Finished:---------Successfully complete ho gaya
Error:------------Execution me problem aayi
Waiting:----------Kisi dependency ka wait kar raha hai
Delegated:--------Kisi aur user ko de diya gaya
Forwarded:--------Next user ko forward kiya gaya
Expired:----------Time khatam ho gaya
Cancelled:--------Manually cancel kiya gaya
Completed:--------Final complete state
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

