🧠 1. setEscalationOwner(String owner):-
👉 Kya karta hai?
Ye define karta hai ki agar WorkItem time pe complete nahi hua (expire ya delay)
→ to kisko escalate karna hai (next person)
🔹 Example:-
WorkItemConfig config = new WorkItemConfig();
config.setEscalationOwner("admin");
👉 Matlab:-
Original owner ne kaam nahi kiya
To WorkItem admin ko transfer ho jayega

🧠 2. getEscalationOwner():-
👉 Kya karta hai?
Jo escalation owner set hai wo return karta hai
String owner = config.getEscalationOwner();
System.out.println(owner); // admin
