---------
🧠 🔷 1. Level kya hota hai?
👉 Level = approval ka stage / hierarchy step
Matlab:-
WorkItem ek hi nahi hota
Multiple approvals ho sakte hain
Har step = ek level
🔥 Simple Example:-
Level1 → Manager Approval
Level2 → Director Approval
Level3 → Admin Approval
👉 Ye sab alag-alag WorkItems ho sakte hain.

🔷 2. Common Levels (Real Project):-
⚠️ Note:-
👉 SailPoint me levels fixed enum nahi hote
👉 Ye mostly custom define hote hain.

✅ Common Naming Convention:-
Level	       Description
Level1	First approval (Manager)
Level2	Second approval (Senior Manager / Director)
Level3	Final approval (Admin / Security)
Level4	Special approval (Audit / Compliance)
----------------------------------------------------------
