👉 setApprovalMode(String mode)
Decide karta hai approval ka logic kaise chalega
config.setApprovalMode("serial");

👉 Common modes:-
serial   → ek ke baad ek
parallel → sab ek sath
any      → kisi ek ka approval enough

👉 getApprovalMode()
String mode = config.getApprovalMode();
