-------
🔥 4. NotificationTemplate kya hai?

👉 NotificationTemplate = email / notification ka design + content

Matlab:

Jab WorkItem create hota hai
System email bhejta hai
Wo email ka format = template
🧠 NotificationTemplate kisse banta hai?

👉 Ye banta hai:

XML configuration
Ya SailPoint UI me define hota hai
🔷 Basic Notification Template Example
<NotificationTemplate name="ApprovalTemplate">
    <Subject>Approval Required</Subject>

    <Body>
        Hello $identity.name,

        You have a pending approval request.

        Please review and take action.

        Thanks,
        SailPoint System
    </Body>
</NotificationTemplate>
🔥 Dynamic Variables (Important)
$identity.name
$workItem.name
$request.id

👉 Ye runtime pe replace ho jate hain
---------------------------------------------------------
